<ul>
  <li>참고 : <a href="https://github.com/kitian616/jekyll-TeXt-theme" target="_blank">TeXt Theme</a><br />
  <img src="/assets/images/blog/JekyllTheme/img09.png" alt="Image" width="600px" /><br />
  <em>출처 : jekyll_TeXt-theme</em></li>
</ul>

<ol>
  <li>install the theme
    <ol>
      <li>common method</li>
      <li>ruby gem method : setup your site 필요</li>
    </ol>
  </li>
  <li>setup your site</li>
  <li>local preview for development, build and publish.</li>
</ol>

<h3 id="install-theme">Install Theme</h3>

<ol>
  <li>
    <dl>
      <dt>fork theme git</dt>
      <dd>git clone을 통해서도 가능</dd>
      <dd>github pages 사용 시 fork로 간단하게 적용 가능하므로 편한 방법을 선택할 것</dd>
    </dl>

    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/kitian616/jekyll-TeXt-theme" target="_blank">jekyll-Text-theme</a> github 방문</li>
      <li>fork git<br />
  <img src="/assets/images/blog/JekyllTheme/img10.png" alt="Image" width="600px" /></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>내 github 설정</p>

    <ul>
      <li>repository rename<br />
  <img src="/assets/images/blog/JekyllTheme/img11.png" alt="Image" width="600px" /></li>
      <li>page 접속 확인<br />
  <img src="/assets/images/blog/JekyllTheme/img12.png" alt="Image" width="600px" /></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

