<h3 id="스킨-설정">스킨 설정</h3>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>text_skin: default # "default" (default), "dark", "forest", "ocean", "chocolate", "orange"
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="mathjax-설정">MathJax 설정</h3>

<h3 id="_configyml">_config.yml</h3>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>## Mathjax
mathjax: true # false (default), true
mathjax_autoNumber: false # false (default), true &lt;&lt; 자동 수식 번호매기기 해제
</code></pre></div></div>

<h4 id="text-align">text align</h4>

<p>mathjax.html &gt; _config에 displayAlign과 displayIndent 추가</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>&lt;script type="text/x-mathjax-config"&gt;
MathJax.Hub.Config({
  displayAlign: "left",
  displayIndent: "2em"
});
&lt;/script&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;script type="text/x-mathjax-config"&gt;
    var _config = { 
        tex2jax: {
            inlineMath: [['$','$'], ['\\(','\\)']]
        },
        displayAlign: "left",
        displayIndent: ".5em"
    };MathJax.Hub.Config(_config);
&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.bootcss.com/mathjax/2.7.4/MathJax.js?config=TeX-MML-AM_CHTML" async&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
</code></p>
